      <title>Hexo 教程（三）评论</title>
      <link href="/2021/07/10/hexo-comments/"/>
      <url>/2021/07/10/hexo-comments/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="安装-Giscus"><a href="#安装-Giscus" class="headerlink" title="安装 Giscus"></a>安装 Giscus</h2><h3 id="开放仓库"><a href="#开放仓库" class="headerlink" title="开放仓库"></a>开放仓库</h3><p><a href="https://github.com/lflwork/lflwork.github.io">https://github.com/lflwork/lflwork.github.io</a></p><p><img src="/images/hexo-comments-01.png"></p><h3 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h3><p>访问：<a href="https://github.com/apps/giscus">https://github.com/apps/giscus</a></p><p><img src="/images/hexo-comments-02.png"></p><p><img src="/images/hexo-comments-03.png"></p><h3 id="启用"><a href="#启用" class="headerlink" title="启用"></a>启用</h3><p><img src="/images/hexo-comments-04.png"></p><p><img src="/images/hexo-comments-05.png"></p><h2 id="检测"><a href="#检测" class="headerlink" title="检测"></a>检测</h2><p>访问：<a href="https://giscus.app/zh-CN">https://giscus.app/zh-CN</a></p><p><img src="/images/hexo-comments-06.png"></p><h3 id="获取配置"><a href="#获取配置" class="headerlink" title="获取配置"></a>获取配置</h3><p><code>data-repo</code><br><code>data-repo-id</code><br><code>data-category-id</code></p><p><img src="/images/hexo-comments-07.png"></p><h2 id="集成"><a href="#集成" class="headerlink" title="集成"></a>集成</h2><h3 id="参数"><a href="#参数" class="headerlink" title="参数"></a>参数</h3><p>修改主题配置文件 _config.butterfly.yml 中对应的三项</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">comments:</span><br><span class="line">  use: Giscus</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># ...  </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Giscus</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># https://giscus.app/</span></span><br><span class="line">giscus:</span><br><span class="line">  repo:</span><br><span class="line">  repo_id:</span><br><span class="line">  category_id:</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/images/hexo-comments-08.png"></p><h3 id="参考资料"><a href="#参考资料" class="headerlink" title="参考资料"></a>参考资料</h3><ul><li><a href="https://butterfly.js.org/posts/ceeb73f/">Butterfly 主题评论</a></li><li><a href="https://giscus.app/zh-CN">Giscus</a></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
